library(corrplot)

# Create helper function to plot
plot_matrix <- function(matrix_toplot){
  corrplot.mixed(matrix_toplot, is.corr = FALSE, 
           order = "original", 
           tl.col='black', tl.cex=.75)
}

Plot the correlations between columns

plot_matrix(cor(data))
